data.description: Welcome to your ideal home, a beautiful 2-story residence nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac. This spacious abode boasts a kitchen equipped with top-notch Bosch appliances, complemented by recent fresh paint throughout, creating a clean and welcoming atmosphere. Find solace in the generous primary bedroom, and embrace energy-efficient living with solar panels installed in 2018. Contribute to a greener lifestyle with rain barrels, and enjoy the modern comforts provided by recent upgrades, including HVAC (2018), roof (2018), gutter leaf stopper (2020), and a water heater (2022). This well-maintained home seamlessly combines modern convenience with exterior charm, offering a tranquil space for you and your family.
